raw.max_input_tokens: max input tokens, if the provider specifies it. if not default to max_tokens
raw.max_output_tokens: max output tokens, if the provider specifies it. if not default to max_tokens
raw.max_tokens: LEGACY parameter. set to max_output_tokens if provider specifies it. IF not set to max_input_tokens, if provider specifies it.
raw.mode: one of: chat, embedding, completion, image_generation, audio_transcription, audio_speech, image_generation, moderation, rerank, search

processed.context_window: LEGACY parameter. set to max_output_tokens if provider specifies it. IF not set to max_input_tokens, if provider specifies it.
